// Under the Skin (NTSC-U)
// File generated by GameHacking.org

[All Items are unlimited with these below codes]
author=bungholio
description=00 - Golden Hammer (can&#039;t be used if you aren&#039;t disguised)
01 - Bruiser
02 - Vanishing Capsule
03 - Gun
04 - T-Rex
05 - RocketLauncher
06 - Camera
07 - Fire Bowling Ball
08 - Holy Circle (It will freeze the game if you use it on any level other than Pranksylvania)
09 - In-Line Skates
0a - Karaoke
0b - Tacks
0c - Electro Bomb
0d - Remote Bomb (you can&#039;t detonate them unless one of your items is the Remote Switch)
0e - Pie
0f - Remote Switch (detonates nothing if you have no remote bombs set)
10 - Virus
11 - Tank
12 - Hula Hoop
13 - Tornado
14 - Fireworks
15 - ???? (the question mark random item, can&#039;t be used unless only 1 item is set to this and no other items are set, but it will work with a joker command)
16 - Torch (doesn&#039;t work without a disguise)
17 - Fart
18 - Elephant
19 - Bowling Ball
1a - Laser Gun
1b - Cannon (stretches your character in a goofy way when you aren&#039;t disguised)
1c - Position Switcher
1d - Vacuum
1e - Coin Color Switcher
1f - Boxing Glove
20 - Hamburger
21 - Bruce
22 - Cosmiman (it seems to mix it&#039;s model with your character&#039;s
23 - Warp (stretches your head higher if you aren&#039;t disguised)
24 - Volcanic Blast
25 - Mob Attack
26 - Lasso
27 - UFO Call
28 - Grudge Missile
29 - Golden Armor (model mixes with your character if you don&#039;t have a disguise)
2a - Magnet Hands
2b - Duel
2c - Double Coins

And these 2 Joker Commands are CMX&#039;s codes. They are useful for switching item digits.
Player 1 Joker Command
D091E502 0000FFFF
Player 2 Joker Command
D091E602 0000FFFF
